text: WRAQ-LP (92.7 FM) is a radio station licensed to serve the community of Angelica, New York. The station is owned by Angelica Community Radio Inc. It airs a variety radio format. The station was assigned the WRAQ-LP call letters by the Federal Communications Commission on February 26, 2014. ==References== ==External links== * Official Website * RAQ-LP RAQ-LP Category:Radio stations established in 2016 Category:2016 establishments in New York (state) Category:Variety radio stations in the United States Category:Allegany County, New York
